creator: Voalte
descriptionHtml:
Voalte Me connects caregivers outside the hospital with Voalte One users inside the hospital. Using personal smartphones, care teams communicate and collaborate via cellular or Wi-Fi connections for access anytime, anywhere. Voalte Me gives doctors and other clinicians a HIPAA-compliant alternative to standard texting.


PLEASE READ BEFORE DOWNLOADING: To use this application your hospital must have the Voalte Server already installed.
descriptionShort: Voalte Me allows care teams to communicate securely anytime, anywhere.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
What's new in Voalte Platform 3.7?
New features and bug fixes!

- Override Do Not Disturb settings: Voalte Platform notifications can override Silent Mode settings.
To enable, launch Voalte Me>Settings>Notifications & Sounds>Enable Override Do Not Disturb.

- New text tones: Change your text tone to a sound of your choice or use the Voalte Platform default.
To enable, launch Voalte Me>Settings>Notifications & Sounds.

Both require 3.7 Voalte Platform Server. Contact Voalte to learn more.

title: Voalte Me

creator: Voalte
descriptionHtml:
Voalte One combines VoIP and video calling, alert notifications, and dynamic text messaging in one app to provide next-generation patient-centered communication. Communicate based on patient, team or unit-level, allowing continuous collaboration across shift-handoffs. Integrate with existing systems to see real-time patient data from the EMR and other medical devices. Respond to bedside alerts and view live streaming waveforms.


PLEASE READ BEFORE DOWNLOADING: To use this application your hospital must have the Voalte Server already installed.
descriptionShort: Voalte Me allows care teams to communicate securely anytime, anywhere.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
What’s New in Voalte Mobile 3.9?

- Chatroom collaboration driven by your patient, team, and unit assignments. See context from caregivers before you and tag in those who need to be a part of the conversation. *
- Receive notifications from all Voalte hospitals you are associated with simultaneously
- Refreshed user interface
- And more!

*Requires Voalte Platform Server 3.9. Please contact your Voalte representative for more information.
